Beskrivning av kaffemaskin

Simpel kaffe masskin med 3 knappar 
och ett mynt in kast och mynt retur under inkastet
Spotar ut koppar
En knapp för svart kaffe 
och en för att få en Cappuccino 
och sista knappen för att få
en varm chocklad.
Maskigen kan växla pengar
5 kr svart kaffe 
8 kr varm chocklad 
10 kr Cappuccino

--------------------------------------

### Properties

poweredAccess (boolean)
- if the machine has powered on

waterAccess (boolean)
- if the machine has acces to water

amountOfCoffe (number) 
- the amount of ground coffee left in grams

amountOfChocolatePowder (number)
- the amount of chocolate powder left in grams

amountOfMilk (number)
- the amount of milk left in cl

numberOfCups (number)
- the amount of cups left in the machine

coffeePerCup (number)
- the amount of grounded coffee per cup in grams

amountOfChocolatePowderPerCup (number)
- the amount of chocolate powder per cup in grams 

cappuccinoMilkPerCup (number)
- the amount of milf in a cappuccino

hotChocolateMilkPerCup (number)
- the amount of milk in a hot cup of chocolate in cl:s

insertedMoney (number)
- that keeps track off the amount of money inserted 
  then resets when the drink have been served



### Methods

checkForPower (boolean)
- check for accses to power

checkForWater (boolean)
- check for accses to water

insertMoney(amount)
- let's the user insert money.
  Returns true if enough money for chosen type of beverage is reached,
  otherwise false.

returnMoney (amount)
- let the user get change

fillWithCoffee (amount)
- fill with ground coffee in grams

fillWithChocolatePowder (amount)
- fill with chocolatepowder in grams

fillWithMilk (amount)
- fill with milk in cl:s

fillWithCups (amount)
- fill the machine with cups

brewBlackcoffee (amount)
- brew blackcoffee
  look att insertedMoney to see if the amount of money is enough

brewCappuccino (amount)
- brew half cup of blackcoffee
  and fill the rest with milk
  look att insertedMoney to see if the amount of money is enough

brewHotChocolate ()
- make hotchocolate
  look att insertedMoney to see if the amount of money is enough

checkCoffee ()
- check so there is enough coffee for a cup

checkChocolatePowder ()
- check so there is enough chocolatepowder for a cup

checkMilk ()
- check so there is enough milk for a cup

checkCups ()
- check so there is enough a cup

dispenseCup ()
- dispense cup